Definition: talk socially without exchanging too much information
Example: the men were sitting in the cafe and shooting the breeze
Synonyms: shoot_the_breeze, chat, noun, communication, confabulate, confabulation, confab, chitchat, chit-chat, chatter, person, chatterer, chaffer, natter, gossip, jaw, claver, visit, visitor, converse, talk, socially, without, exchanging, too, much, information, the, men, were, sitting, in, cafe, and, shooting, breeze
Frame: 2
Category: verb.communication
